Description: Haruhi, a poor girl at a rich school, is forced to work – as a boy – for the school’s all-male club. The series is described as a “romantic comedy.”
Title: OURAN HIGH SCHOOL HOST CLUB, VOL. 14
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: The origins and true nature of Pain, Naruto’s arch nemesis, are revealed.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 48
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.” In this volume, Luffy tries to rescue his brother from Naval prison.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 54
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Aang, the last of the airbenders, returns to unify his world and its elemental factions.
Title: THE LAST AIRBENDER (9780345518552)
Author: Dave Roman, Joon Choi and Alison Wilgus
Contributor: by Dave Roman, Joon Choi and Alison Wilgus

Description: The battle for Cross Academy continues as Headmaster Cross enters the fray.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 10
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 2
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: A tournament of champions will decide who is going to be named Shaman King. Will the honorable fighting of Yoh Asakura put him at a disadvantage when he faces the quick and dirty Tao Ren?
Title: SHAMAN KING, VOL. 29
Author: Hiroyuki Takei

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 1
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: This comic tells the story of two women who become friends “in a whirlwind world of sex, music, fashion, gossip and all-night parties!“
Title: NANA, VOL. 21
Author: Ai Yazawa

Description: Sumi is caught between her marital commitment and interest from her husband’s childhood friend.
Title: STEPPING ON ROSES, VOL. 2
Author: Rinko Ueda
